The Professional Certificate Programme in Digital Strategy and Transformation from IIM Kozhikode intends to enhance the skills of the participants in understanding and creating digital ecosystems using various digital technologies like Big Data Analytics, Artificial Intelligence, 3-D Printing, etc. The course will help learners lead the digital transformation journey through efficiency, agility and resilient process capabilities.

